{"tid":394254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於明白點解恭喜蓮子魂歸西天係涼薄","createTime":"2017-09-09T18:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T23:57:07.000Z","uid":54481,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c6895240579ed1d312b74ae37cf4e4329e39d02","tid":394254,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:52:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">基督徒：自殺既人係要落地獄嫁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">所以你如果恭喜魂歸西天，就係串緊佢<br />\n恭喜落地獄先係正確既陳述，任何人都唔應該扭曲事實</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以劉曉波果句係完全冇問題既，因為自然病死，可以魂歸西天<br />\n校方個句「極度遺憾」如無意外應該係講緊共黨唔應該軟禁劉霞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fsin2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21432911_1606833892715988_2209855986758275007_n.jpg?oh=92042ace4e1f0dbf8b9d66192b0bd7a7&amp;oe=5A19C4D2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fsin2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21432911_1606833892715988_2209855986758275007_n.jpg%3Foh%3D92042ace4e1f0dbf8b9d66192b0bd7a7%26oe%3D5A19C4D2&h=c9e8921e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"289a4c2905a3512dd7e44293f2f2314a63fa1e49","tid":394254,"uid":54481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32ae0e19090baed6cb2b25d9ca20eab31cd0f91","tid":394254,"uid":72167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17de0eb0574bdb10bdc9eea193fb6697df3148c","tid":394254,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f03209a43bdb2f8e9f5824bfbcc076c4024b4f5","tid":394254,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"